    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SKY HARBOR AIRPORT\nMunicipal Airport\nPhoenix, Arizona\nThe\nunusual tubular\ncontrol tower,\none\nof\nthe\nworld's largest, is 107 feet high and nine feet in\ndiameter.\nThe airport\nwas built\nat a cost\nof\nwell-over one million dollars and accommodates\nthe landings of more than 50 scheduled airlines\ndaily.\nBarber shop, gift shop and restaurant are\nwithin the terminal building.\nColor Photo by Bob Van Luchene\n34264\n201"
    ],
